    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its size, detailed design, and location, would result in an obtrusive, incongruous, and incompatible form of development that would fail to respect the integrity of the subject property, the terrace of which it forms part, and the wider area. As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and D4 (Delivering good design) of The London Plan (2021) and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020), and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
